INSERT INTO public.user_master (
    first_name,
    last_name,
    user_city,
    user_state,
    user_zip_code,
    user_phone_number,
    user_company,
    business_type,
    user_activated,
    address,
    user_email,
    password
)
VALUES (
    '{{firstName.value}}',
    '{{lastName.value}}',
    '{{city.value}}',
    '{{state.value}}',
    '{{zipCode.value}}',
    '{{Phone.value}}',
    '{{companyName.value}}',
    '{{businessType.value}}',
    true,
    '{{address.value}}',
    '{{newEmail.value}}',
    '{{passBcrypt.data}}'
);
